      "title": "Return to the backbenches: 2018–2019",
      "depth": 1,
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "By resigning as foreign secretary, Johnson returned to the role of a backbench MP.",
              "links": [
                {
                  "text": "backbench MP",
                  "type": "internal",
                  "page": "backbench MP"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "In July, he delivered a resignation speech, stating that ministers were \"saying one thing to the EU about what we are really doing, and pretending another to the electorate\"."
